title:
Make a difference!
Partake in charitable skydiving!
text:
Become a part of a solution to the world's challenges through participation and skydiving for the
sake of the charity just at $50. You only have to select the charity date from the calendar and raise at
least the minimum fund-raising sum. We work with more than 100 charities all over the country.
Over 2000 people each year choose the tandem skydiving with SkydiveBirds club for charity. It's
always very pleasant to help somebody in need and in such an extraordinary way.
